Q1. Simulate a Cybersecurity Incident & Execute Response Plan (10 Marks)
Scenario
An employee reports their computer is slow and showing ransom note. The file server also has encrypted files.

Incident Response Plan Execution
Step	Action
1. Detect	Alert from employee + unusual file encryption alerts from EDR
2. Contain	Disconnect infected PC from network. Shut down file server. Block ransomware C2 IPs at firewall.
3. Investigate	Check which files were encrypted. Find entry point (phishing email with malicious attachment).
4. Eradicate	Remove malware. Delete malicious files. Disable compromised user accounts.
5. Recover	Restore file server from clean backup. Reimage infected PC.
6. Communicate	Notify management. Update employees about phishing threat.

